---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');

const post = {
  title: 'PM Surya Ghar Muft Bijli Yojana: Your Complete Subsidy Guide',
  date: '8 November 2024',
  category: 'Government Schemes',
  readTime: '7 min read',
  author: 'Rayenna Energy Team',
};
---
<Layout title={`${post.title} — Rayenna Energy Blog`} description="The government's free electricity scheme offers up to ₹78,000 in subsidies. Here's exactly how to apply and what to expect.">

  <section class="post-hero">
    <div class="container post-hero__inner">
      <a href={`${base}/blog`} class="back-link">← Back to Blog</a>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-category">{post.category}</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>{post.readTime}</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>{post.date}</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="post-hero__title">{post.title}</h1>
      <div class="post-author">
        <div class="author-avatar">☀</div>
        <div>
          <strong>{post.author}</strong>
          <span>Rayenna Energy, Kochi</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-hero__wave">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M0,30 C360,60 1080,0 1440,30 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#f8f9fa"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding:var(--section-padding); background:var(--color-light)">
    <div class="container post-layout">

      <article class="post-content">
        <p class="post-lead">The PM Surya Ghar Muft Bijli Yojana is the central government's flagship solar subsidy scheme, offering up to <strong>₹78,000 in direct subsidies</strong> for residential solar installations. Here's everything you need to know to apply and get the maximum benefit.</p>

        <h2>What Is PM Surya Ghar Muft Bijli Yojana?</h2>
        <p>Launched in February 2024, this scheme aims to install rooftop solar panels on 1 crore households across India, providing up to 300 units of free electricity per month. The government directly transfers the subsidy to your bank account after installation.</p>

        <h2>Subsidy Amount Breakdown</h2>
        <div class="cost-table">
          <div class="cost-row cost-row--header">
            <span>System Size</span><span>Central Subsidy</span><span>Additional State Subsidy (Kerala)</span><span>Total Benefit</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-row">
            <span>1 kW</span><span>₹30,000</span><span>₹15,000</span><span>₹45,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-row">
            <span>2 kW</span><span>₹60,000</span><span>₹15,000</span><span>₹75,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-row">
            <span>3 kW</span><span>₹78,000</span><span>₹15,000</span><span>₹93,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-row">
            <span>&gt;3 kW</span><span>₹78,000 (capped)</span><span>₹15,000</span><span>₹93,000</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="post-callout">
          <span class="callout-icon">🏛</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Important Note</strong>
            <p>The central subsidy is capped at 3 kW capacity. Even if you install a 5 kW or 10 kW system, the maximum central subsidy remains ₹78,000.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
        <ul class="post-list">
          <li>You must own the residential property where solar panels will be installed.</li>
          <li>The property must have a valid electricity connection (KSEB in Kerala).</li>
          <li>The rooftop must be structurally suitable for solar panel installation.</li>
          <li>Installation must be done through a MNRE-empanelled vendor (like Rayenna Energy).</li>
          <li>The system must be grid-connected (off-grid systems are not eligible).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How to Apply: Step-by-Step</h2>
        <ul class="post-list">
          <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Register on the PM Surya Ghar portal at pmsuryaghar.gov.in using your mobile number and electricity consumer number.</li>
          <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Apply for rooftop solar under your DISCOM (KSEB for Kerala residents).</li>
          <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Get a feasibility approval from KSEB (typically within 15–30 days).</li>
          <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Install the solar system through an empanelled vendor. Rayenna Energy handles this for you.</li>
          <li><strong>Step 5:</strong> Get net metering installed and obtain the commissioning certificate from KSEB.</li>
          <li><strong>Step 6:</strong> Submit the commissioning certificate and bank details on the portal. The subsidy is credited within 30 days.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Timeline to Expect</h2>
        <p>From application to subsidy credit, the typical timeline is <strong>45–90 days</strong>. Rayenna Energy manages the entire process on your behalf, including portal registration, KSEB coordination, and documentation — so you don't have to navigate the bureaucracy alone.</p>

        <div class="post-cta">
          <h3>Let Us Handle Your Subsidy Application</h3>
          <p>Rayenna Energy is an MNRE-empanelled vendor. We manage the entire PM Surya Ghar application process for our customers — at no extra charge.</p>
          <a href={`${base}/contact`} class="btn btn-primary">Book a Free Consultation →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <aside class="post-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Get a Free Quote</h4>
          <p>Talk to our solar experts. No obligation, no pressure.</p>
          <a href={`${base}/contact`} class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%; justify-content:center; margin-top:16px">Request Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Related Articles</h4>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href={`${base}/blog/how-much-does-solar-cost-in-kerala`}>Solar System Cost in Kerala →</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}/blog/solar-vs-electricity-bill-comparison`}>Solar vs KSEB Bill Comparison →</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}/blog/net-metering-explained`}>Net Metering Explained →</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-card--cta">
          <div style="font-size:3rem; margin-bottom:12px">🏛</div>
          <strong>Up to ₹78,000 Subsidy</strong>
          <p>Don't miss out on the government's generous solar subsidy. Apply before the scheme closes.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
.post-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27324f 0%, #3a4a6b 100%);
  padding: 120px 0 80px;
  position: relative;
}
.post-hero__inner { max-width: 860px; }
.back-link {
  display: inline-block;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  transition: color var(--transition);
}
.back-link:hover { color: var(--color-primary); }
.post-meta {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.post-category {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: white;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-weight: 700;
}
.post-hero__title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: white;
  line-height: 1.25;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.post-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
.author-avatar {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
}
.post-author strong { display: block; color: white; font-family: var(--font-heading); }
.post-author span { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
.post-hero__wave { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; line-height: 0; }
.post-hero__wave svg { width: 100%; display: block; }

.post-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
  gap: 48px;
  align-items: start;
}
.post-content { background: white; border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 48px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
.post-lead {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  padding-left: 20px;
}
.post-content h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin: 32px 0 16px;
}
.post-content p { color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; }

.cost-table { border-radius: var(--radius-sm); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin: 20px 0 28px; }
.cost-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr 1.5fr 1fr; gap: 0; }
.cost-row span { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 0.88rem; }
.cost-row--header span { background: var(--color-secondary); color: white; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; }
.cost-row:not(.cost-row--header):nth-child(even) span { background: var(--color-light); }

.post-callout {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  background: var(--color-primary-light);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  padding: 20px;
  margin: 24px 0;
}
.callout-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.post-callout strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-heading); color: var(--color-secondary); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.post-callout p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0; }

.post-list { list-style: none; margin: 16px 0 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
.post-list li { padding-left: 20px; position: relative; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; }
.post-list li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 700; }

.post-cta {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy), #3a4a6b);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 32px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  text-align: center;
}
.post-cta h3 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.post-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 20px; }

.post-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; position: sticky; top: 88px; }
.sidebar-card {
  background: white;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 24px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}
.sidebar-card h4 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-secondary); margin-bottom: 10px; }
.sidebar-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
.sidebar-card--cta { background: var(--color-primary-light); text-align: center; }
.sidebar-card--cta strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-heading); color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.sidebar-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-top: 12px; }
.sidebar-links a { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; transition: text-decoration var(--transition); }
.sidebar-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .post-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .post-sidebar { position: static; }
  .cost-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .cost-row--header span:nth-child(n+3) { display: none; }
  .cost-row span:nth-child(n+3) { display: none; }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .post-content { padding: 24px; }
}
</style>
